Of course. My name is Sarah Johnson.

Sure, it's four five six seven eight nine two.

You're welcome, Sarah. If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. If not, I can help you with anything else you might need.

No, that's all for now. Thank you, Tom.

Thank you for your time, Sarah. If you need further assistance, don't hesitate to call us back. Have a great day!
